data.description: Charming home nestled in Mint Hill, with a welcoming front porch, an open living & dining areas featuring built-ins & electric fireplace. The primary suite is a sanctuary with another fireplace, walk-in closet, & bath including a dual vanity, soaking tub, & river pebble floored shower. The kitchen has granite countertops, tile backsplash, stainless appliances, & gas range, complemented by a cozy breakfast bar. Additional main floor amenities include 2 bedrooms & a full bath, while the upper level offers a spacious bonus room, another bedroom, full bath, & ample storage. Enjoy outdoor living with a covered back patio, fenced yard, & a beautiful inground pool. Also featured is an attached side-entry garage with tons of storage, & a detached climate controlled garage with workshop, plus a separate living quarters complete with a room & bath downstairs, plus kitchenette & living area upstairs. With two driveways, tons of upgrades & NO HOA this property offers endless possibilities.
